Here's the modified `shift` function with the explicit check:
````
function shift(
    TrimmedAmount memory amount,
    uint8 toDecimals
) internal pure returns (TrimmedAmount memory) {
    uint8 actualToDecimals = minUint8(TRIMMED_DECIMALS, toDecimals);
    uint64 scaledAmount = scale(amount.amount, amount.decimals, actualToDecimals);
    if (scaledAmount > type(uint64).max) {
